(1, 'About Us', '<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<h1>The Brains<br />\r\nBehind SuperPad</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SuperPad wasn&rsquo;t built in a day. Neither would we say our team is a rigid fixed team, we are different coders, crypto-enthusiasts, creatives, designers and all of us are buidlers that are pushing forward the revolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our advisors, community and users are crucial parts of our ecosystem and making it as responsive, efficient and damn right epic as possible!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a medley of makers that power Biconomy to power you! Think of our team as the fuel pumpers, to your supercharged car.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Team :- </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arpit jain [CEO &amp; Founder] :- </strong>6 years Experience in Crypto Industry. And 7 years experience in Ecommerce filed . Founder of 24eshop ecommerce portal. Deep expertise in crypto Mining.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Akshat Jain [Co-Founder &amp; CTO ]:- </strong>2 years Experience in crypto industry . 2 years experience in startup management</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Yogesh Saroya [Senior Full Stack Developer] :- </strong>Web developer specializing in Front End / Back End Development. Experienced with all stages of the development cycle for dynamic web projects. well versed in numerous programing languages including JavaScript, MySQL, jQuery, Ajax. Strong Background in project Management and customer relations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ayan Jain [Blockchain Developer]:- </strong>1 Year experience in blockchain smart contracts development | IIT Delhi .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nidhi Sethiya [Ui/UX Desginer] :- </strong>3 Years experience in UI/UX design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Atul Dugeriya [ Graphic Designer] :- </strong>3 years experience in Graphic Designing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arpit Dungerwal [ Account Manager ]:-</strong> <strong> </strong>4 Years Working Experience In UAE with reupdated company As a Credit controller &amp; Account head.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chirag Thug [Content manager]:- </strong>2 Years experience in content writing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ayushi [ Social Media Manager ]:- </strong> 2 Years Experience in social media managing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>karan singh [Digital marketing Manager] :- </strong>4 years experience in digital marketing field .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Join Our Team Contact :- support@superpad.finance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'About Us', 'about us', 'about-us', 2, 'Company', '2022-03-20 14:48:48', '2022-03-27 17:18:13');
